com.ibm.jaggr.core.impl.module

Class ModuleCacheImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.jaggr.core.impl.module.ModuleCacheImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IModuleCache, Serializable

    public class ModuleCacheImpl
extends Object
implements IModuleCache, Serializable
    This class implements the IModuleCache interface by extending ConcurrentHashMap and adds methods for cloning and dumping the cache contents.
